    @Extension
public static final class EnvironmentBuildPlugin.DescriptorImpl
extends hudson.tasks.BuildStepDescriptor<hudson.tasks.Builder>
    Descriptor for EBSAReleasePlugin. Used as a singleton. The class is marked as public so that it can be accessed from views.

    See src/main/resources/hudson/plugins/hello_world/HelloWorldBuilder/*.jelly for the actual HTML fragment for the configuration screen.
